title: ‘Caravan’ makes last stop before reaching final destination
text:
‘Caravan’ makes last stop before reaching final destination Saturday, April 07, 2018 - 01:36 
A “caravan” of Central American migrants pressed on through Mexico on Friday, greatly diminished in size a day after hundreds of exhausted members left a field where they had been stranded all week.
